{"type":"text","timestamp":1775891337610,"sessionID":"ses_284a3f022ffepV3qnah8C7bRgF","part":{"id":"prt_d7b5f4947001uNk8br6nGDttGQ","messageID":"msg_d7b5f40d0001CG1VM5TIWB3ddG","sessionID":"ses_284a3f022ffepV3qnah8C7bRgF","type":"text","text":"Successfully created proposal.md for AR-038 — Go 单元测试 (workloadmanager).\n\nThe proposal covers:\n\n- **Purpose**: Comprehensive unit testing strategy for critical reconciliation logic\n- **Scope**: Controller reconciler components (codeinterpreter.go, status.go, finalizers.go, predicates.go, errors.go, controller.go), sandbox handler, and server setup\n- **Coverage targets**: 80-95% depending on component priority\n- **Test strategy**: Unit tests with fake clients, table-driven tests, behavior testing\n- **Implementation plan**: 5-week phased approach from core utilities to validation\n- **CI/CD integration**: Pre-commit checks, coverage thresholds, pipeline requirements\n\nTotal: 472 lines with detailed test scenarios for 8 test files covering 80+ test cases.","time":{"start":1775891337609,"end":1775891337609}}}
